snippet.title: HALF-LIFE mod: Mistake || No Commentary || Full Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This mod will let us into a horroristic world in the Andrew Parker asylum and we will live through (or not) in the view of a mental patient.
The mod's primal object is not the insane bloodbath. The real object is to escape from the huge building which holds a lot of secrets.
#halflife #halflifeMOD #half-life1
